Text:
@Rhine86
The game works good, but has lots of issues still without the 4th patch. (One advantage of purchase, support and easy access to patches)

A few things to check if you're not able to even start. Make sure you have installed the DirectX, VB, and C++ installations that came with the game (located in the installation directory). The game will error out or crash or not even start if any one of those is missing.
